            <p>Nous pr√©parons du contenu de qualit√© pour t'aider √† transformer ta vie. Reviens bient√¥t pour d√©couvrir nos premiers articles sur la reprogrammation du subconscient.</p>
                         <div class="newsletter-reminder">
               <p>üí° <strong>Conseil :</strong> Abonne-toi √† notre newsletter pour √™tre notifi√© d√®s qu'un nouvel article sera publi√©.</p>
             </div>
          </div>
        )}
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .blog-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding-top: 100px;
  }

  .blog-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 20px 60px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .blog-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #636366 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #8E8E93;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .search-filters {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px 60px;
  }

  .search-bar {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 30px;
  }

  .search-icon {
    position: absolute;
    left: 20px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    color: #8E8E93;
  }

  .search-input {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 16px 20px 16px 50px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 100px;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    font-size: 16px;
    outline: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .search-input::placeholder {
    color: #8E8E93;
  }

  .search-input:focus {
    border-color: #007AFF;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.1);
  }

  /* √âtats de la barre de recherche */
  .search-bar.searching .search-input {
    border-color: #007AFF;
    background: rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.1);
  }
  
  .search-bar.searching .search-icon {
    color: #007AFF;
  }
  
  .search-bar:focus-within .search-icon {
    color: #007AFF;
  }

  .search-results {
    position: absolute;
    right: 16px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    background: rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.1);
    color: #007AFF;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    display: none;
  }
  
  .search-results.visible {
    display: block;
  }

  .category-filters {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .filter-btn {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 100px;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .filter-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .filter-btn.active {
    background: #007AFF;
    border-color: #007AFF;
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .articles-section {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px 80px;
  }

  .articles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 400px));
    gap: 30px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .article-card {
    background: #272729;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .article-card:hover {
    background: #2C2C2E;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .article-link {
    display: block;
